      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a concourse-level E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS. This example boasts a pristine subframe with documented reinforcement, a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Recent compression and leak-down tests confirm optimal cylinder health and thermal efficiency. The chassis dynamics are sharpened by fresh bushings and a perfectly calibrated suspension, ensuring the high-revving power delivery is matched by surgical handling. Zero deferred maintenance, flawless paint depth, and a cabin that retains its factory-fresh tactile feel. A true driver\u2019s specimen in impeccable, collector-grade condition.",
      "price": 47500.0,
