    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the 'showroom new' experience. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a drop of rain or a winter road. The exterior paint is deep and lustrous, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with zero stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no visible bolster wear, and the original factory scent still lingers. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a full-service history exclusively through authorized dealerships. The engine bay is spotless, and the undercarriage is as clean as the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in concours-level condition without the new-car depreciation. Serious inquiries only for this investment-grade example.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
